data.description: Pristine 5-acre lot near Floresville, Texas, where the allure of country living meets the convenience of a quick commute to San Antonio. This expansive parcel has been cleared, creating an ideal canvas for your dream home or investment venture.  One of the notable features of this lot is its freedom from restrictive covenants, offering you the flexibility to build and design as you envision. Water and electricity are readily available at the road, streamlining the building process and enhancing the overall convenience of this prime real estate.  Immerse yourself in the tranquility of country living, where the open expanse of this lot invites you to create your own haven. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a strategic investment, this property near Floresville, Texas, offers limitless possibilities in a location that seamlessly blends rural charm with urban accessibility. Don't miss the chance to make this expansive and unrestricted canvas your own. No HOA!
